metadata.name: London #1
metadata.description:
London 2022.

Architecture defines our environment and our lives. 

Well-designed cities add richness to our everyday and have the opportunity to surprise, excite and reward us. Museums, concert halls and transport infrastructure engage in large numbers f people and we all like to feel treated as individuals.

Cities are places of motion and buildings are central to the ebb and flow of their populations on a daily, weekly and annual basis. I see buildings as places of motion, overviewing the passing of time without comment but with a positive engagement.

5669 x 3780 px

Date of creation 2022.
Not for commercial use.
